title: Gauri Shankar Vegetarian Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, International, Beer/Wine
description: Cafe attached to Gauri Shankar Guest House. Small range of dishes that rotates regularly. Library and a quaint garden to sit in are available. Try the Nepali national dish, dal bhaat takali, upon request. Directions: Go down the street near Gauri Ghat that is across from the Ghat.
